reviewText:
Speaking of Resident Evil 4, I want to just yell at each corner - a masterpiece, a revolution in gaming, etc. I note a few words about the game itself. What you need to know to modern gamers:
- A game which is ahead of its time, even now, the game is played just fine;
- For the first time people start the game will be a surprise in the form of Challenge;
- A huge variety of gaming moments;
- An interesting story.
And much more. It makes no sense to talk a lot as it is necessary to look for another gamer who has not played this game.
About remaster - it is excellent. Here is excellent, reworked control, which finally did sane on the PC. Level graphics - GC (that the praise remaster) with some twists such as filters, shadows and mastareys 60 fps .... and it's all a matter of fact. And it's wonderful. This is all the exact same game we all love, in the best version, and I recommend it to all, an unequivocal masterpiece for the ages.
